     to FTFP at 4-5 GeV. No LEP for inelastic for p,n,pi,K.
-  G4LEPNeutronBuilder.cc: when limit for MaxInelastic is 0, do NOT add 
     LEP for inelastic; needed by above FTFP_BERT.

